mc.server.types

Class TypeVectorInt

  • java.lang.Object
    • mc.server.types.TypeVectorInt

  • public class TypeVectorInt
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines a TypeVectorInt object.

    Provides methods to read a Integer vector, vector serialization and deserialization methods, and finally standard multiplication methods.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Malhar Chaudhari
